data.title: Central Bank of Ireland
data.meta_description: Contact details for the Central Bank of Ireland and other important contacts can be found on this web page.
data.text:
Email: You can contact Central Bank of Ireland via [email protected]. We are currently busier than usual and it may take up to 15 working days to reply to your email. If your query is urgent, call us using the numbers below. You can also find answers to common questions in our Consumer Hub.

Phone: 0818 681 681 or +353 (0)1 224 5800

Phone lines are open Monday to Friday, 09.00 - 17.00.
